The [[Allmusic]] review awarded the album 4½ stars stating "McPherson is in top form".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/live-in-tokyo-mw0000909298 Allmusic Review] accessed April 24, 2014</ref>

== Track listing ==
''All compositions by Charles McPherson except as indicated''
# "Tokyo Blue" - 7:14  
# "[[East of the Sun (and West of the Moon)|East of the Sun]]" ([[Brooks Bowman]]) - 5:32  
# "[[Desafinado]]" ([[Antonio Carlos Jobim]], [[Newton Mendonça]]) - 8:32  
# "Orient Express" - 9:13  
# "[[These Foolish Things (Remind Me of You)|These Foolish Things]]" ([[Eric Maschwitz]], [[Jack Strachey]], [[Harry Link]]) -  6:18
# "[[Bouncing with Bud]]" ([[Bud Powell]]) - 6:34

